nodes.title: LLM Model Load
widgets_values:
You are an assistant who describes the content and style of images. 
                    Describe only what you see in the image, not what you think the image is about.Be factual and literal. 
                    Do not use metaphors or similes. 
                    Be concise.
Return a list of danbooru tags for this image, formatted as lowercase, separated by commas.

1. Go to the setting icon (at the right of Queue Size on the panel)

4. Wich toggles to show = bypass only
